<task id="UDSS-015a" project="UI Dialog Shell Standardization">
  <metadata>
    <title>Extract FindSimilar dialog to shared library</title>
    <status>not-started</status>
    <phase>2</phase>
    <estimated-effort>3 hours</estimated-effort>
    <tags>shared-library, dialog, extraction, find-similar</tags>
    <dependencies>001, 002</dependencies>
    <parallel-group>P2-extract</parallel-group>
  </metadata>
  <prompt>Move the FindSimilar dialog (4 files) from the Corporate Workspace into @spaarke/ui-components as a shared component. Refactor all data services to use the IDataService abstraction instead of direct Xrm.WebApi calls. Create a local index.ts for the component folder but do NOT touch the shared library barrel export (components/index.ts) — that is owned by task 011b.</prompt>
  <role>Frontend developer with expertise in React 19, Fluent UI v9, and Dataverse Code Pages</role>
  <goal>FindSimilar dialog lives in @spaarke/ui-components/components/FindSimilarDialog/ with IDataService abstraction, compiles cleanly via tsc, and is ready for barrel export</goal>
  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-012">Services must use IDataService abstraction, no direct webApi</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-026">Vite + vite-plugin-singlefile for Code Pages</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-021">Fluent v9 tokens only, React 19, dark mode required</constraint>
    <constraint source="parallel-safety">ONLY modify files within your designated folder — do NOT touch shared barrel exports (components/index.ts)</constraint>
    <constraint source="parallel-safety">File ownership: ONLY components/FindSimilarDialog/ folder. No other folders may be created or modified.</constraint>
  </constraints>
  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>.claude/adr/ADR-012-shared-components.md</file>
      <file>.claude/adr/ADR-026-full-page-custom-page-standard.md</file>
      <file>.claude/adr/ADR-021-fluent-v9-design-system.md</file>
      <file>docs/guides/SHARED-UI-COMPONENTS-GUIDE.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>
  <steps>
    <step id="1">Identify the 4 FindSimilar dialog files in the Corporate Workspace source</step>
    <step id="2">Create target folder: src/client/shared/Spaarke.UI.Components/src/components/FindSimilarDialog/</step>
    <step id="3">Move all 4 files into the new folder, preserving directory structure</step>
    <step id="4">Refactor all data service calls to accept IDataService parameter instead of calling Xrm.WebApi directly</step>
    <step id="5">Update all internal imports to use relative paths within the component folder</step>
    <step id="6">Create local index.ts that exports the dialog component and any public types</step>
    <step id="7">Run tsc to verify the component compiles without errors</step>
    <step id="8">Verify no Xrm.WebApi references remain in the extracted files</step>
  </steps>
  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion>All 4 FindSimilar files exist in components/FindSimilarDialog/</criterion>
    <criterion>All data services use IDataService abstraction — zero direct Xrm.WebApi calls</criterion>
    <criterion>Local index.ts exports the dialog component</criterion>
    <criterion>tsc compiles without errors</criterion>
    <criterion>No files outside components/FindSimilarDialog/ were modified</criterion>
    <criterion>components/index.ts (barrel) was NOT touched</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
</task>
